item.description:
You can upload field metadata for a System in a zipped JSON file using the upload option on the System detail page.
Fields JSON Import File Format Use the following schema information to format the JSON file that is used to load field metadata for a System.
Format:
{
&quot;version&quot;: &quot;2018-02-07&quot;,
&quot;fields&quot;:[
{
&quot;name&quot;: &quot;...&quot;,
&quot;location&quot;: {...},
&quot;type&quot;: {..}
}
]
}
 You can request a sample JSON file by submitting a request to support.
